  <div class="home-text">
    <br><br><br>
    <h2> It starts with a dream </h2>
    <br>
    <p> It all starts when someone in Africa has the courage to follow a dream. A dream of starting a business that breaks the cycle of poverty and generates lasting economic independence. </p>
  </div>
  <img id="thoughts-img" src="<%= asset_path("thoughts.png") %>" data-sr="enter top move 50px over 1s">
