<div class="wide-container bg2">
  <div class="home-text">
    <br><br>
    <h2> A fresh new approach </h2>
    <br>
    <p> At Elevate Africa, we help startups get their dreams off the ground. Our unique startup accelerator model surrounds entrepreneurs with a combination of business training, mentoring, microfinance and technology to help their businesses succeed. </p>
  </div>
  <img id="bg3-img" src="<%= asset_path("rita3.png") %>" data-sr="enter bottom move 100px over 1s">
</div>
<div class="wide-container bg3">
  <div class="home-text">
    <br>
    <h2> Startups that change the game </h2>
    <br>
    <p> We like to invest in innovative businesses that make a difference for families and communities on multiple levels. Our entrepreneurs do everything from making soap that protects against malaria, to building solar ovens that save money and help protect the environment at the same time. </p>
  </div>
  <img id="bg2-img" src="<%= asset_path("rita2.png") %>" data-sr="enter left move 100px over 1s">
</div>
<div class="wide-container bg4">
  <div class="home-text">
    <br>
    <h2> Grow, expand, and create new jobs </h2>
    <br>
    <p> When an Elevate Africa entrepreneur pays back her loan, that same money goes back into the loan pool to help the next group of entrepreneurs. Or to fund the expansion of her growing business with a new loan. It’s an amazing multiplier effect that means even a small donation can impact 10s, 100s, or even 1000s of people over time. </p>
  </div>
  <img id="rise-img" src="<%= asset_path("rise.png") %>" data-sr="enter right move 50px over 1s">
</div>
<div class="wide-container bg5">
  <div class="home-text">
    <br>
    <h2> And change lives </h2>
    <br>
    <p> Proceeds from these businesses help put food on the table, buy medicine for the baby, and give kids the gift of education. Since nearly 80 percent of our entrepreneurs are women, we’re also helping to change a few minds along the way. </p>
  </div>
  <img id="student-img" src="<%= asset_path("students.png") %>" data-sr="enter left move 50px over 1s">
</div>
<div class="wide-container" id="footer-banner">
  <div class="medium-container padding-center">
    <h1> JOIN THE ADVENTURE </h1>
    <p id="home-blurb"> We think we’re onto something pretty big here at Elevate Africa. We see it every day in the eyes of talented entrepreneurs across Africa who have the vision, optimism and courage to create a better life for themselves. People who are just crazy enough to share our dream of a world where innovation and self-reliance really do triumph over poverty. We invite you to join our adventure today. </p>
  </div>
  <a class="button about-button" href="<%= about_path %>"> Learn More </a>
  <a class="button about-button" onclick="<%= new_donation_path %>"> Donate</a>
</div>
<script src="<%= asset_path("scrollReveal.min.js") %>"></script>
<script>
  window.sr = new scrollReveal();
  $(window).scroll(function() {
    var startScroll = $(".bg1").offset().top - 260;
    var truck = $(".bg4").offset().top + 400 - $(window).height();
    var topScroll = $(".bg5").offset().top + 500 - $(window).height();
    if ($(window).scrollTop() > topScroll) {
      $("#bg1-img").addClass("bg1-edit");
      $("#bg1-img").removeClass("bg1-begin");
    } else if ($(window).scrollTop() < startScroll) {
      $("#bg1-img").addClass("bg1-begin");
      $("#bg1-img").removeClass("bg1-edit");
    } else {
      $("#bg1-img").removeClass("bg1-edit");
      $("#bg1-img").removeClass("bg1-begin");
    }
    if ($(window).scrollTop() > truck && $(window).scrollTop() < truck + 500) {
      $("#bg1-img").addClass("flip");
    } else {
      $("#bg1-img").removeClass("flip");
    }
  })
</script>
